<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202825>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 9. Gymnolaelaps messor sp. nov., female. 1. dorsal shield; 2. dorsal seta Zx enlarged; 3. ventral idiosoma; 4. hypostome; 5. palp tarsal claw; 6. epistome; 7. chelicera; 8 genu III, dorsal aspect; 9. genu and tibia IV, dorsal aspect. Scale bar = 100 μm for 1 and 3, 50 μm for 4, 6, 7; 10 μm for 5. Figure 2 not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202825/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

